- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper utilizes deep reinforcement learning techniques. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a potential category as the paper deals with resource management in a network system. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is also a possible category as the paper deals with optimizing the allocation of bandwidth in a network system.
